A brief description of what you will find in each directory and/or what you are expected to put in.

- bin: all the executables must be put in this directory.
- cuda: all the CUDA sources must be put in this directory.
- images: the set of images to test the application.
- include: the includes of the used libraries, leave this directory as it is.
- Makefile.inc: General definitions for make, you should touch this unless this templace directory is in a non-standard place.
- sequential: the reference implementation, read the code carefully and use the same structure for your code.
- src: the source code of the used libraries, leave this directory as it is.
